Package pacman.algorithms

This package defines the algorithm of pacman and ghost in the maze.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAlgorithm
    Contains the algorithm of pacman and ghost in the maze.
    AlgorithmFactory
    Defines an utility for creating algorithms.
    AlgorithmFactory.SupportedAlgorithms
    Contains the list of supported algorithms in this application.
    AlgorithmsUtility
    Contains utilities that will be used in pacman algorithms.
    AStarAlgorithm
    Defines an algorithm that let the agent applies the A* search algorithm at each step.
    DfsAlgorithm
    Defines an algorithm that let the agent applies the dfs algorithm at each step: the agent does not change its current direction unless it has to.
    GreedyAlgorithm
    Defines an algorithm that let the agent applies the greedy search algorithm at each step.
    MinimaxAlgorithm
    Defines an algorithm that let the agent applies the minimax algorithm at each step.
    NullAlgorithm
    Defines an algorithm that let the agent stay still at any time.
    RandomSelectionAlgorithm
    Defines an algorithm that let the agent random choose an action at each step.

Package pacman.algorithms Description

This package defines the algorithm of pacman and ghost in the maze. The search is mainly BFS and A star.
Version:
1.0
